5_8	0.0	ADHD has only within the last few years been recognized as a legitimate adult diagnosis.
5_9	0.0	``A lot of people were trained that people outgrew ADHD,'' said Dr.
5_10	0.0	Russell Barkley, director of psychology and professor of psychiatry and neurology at the University of Massachusetts Medical School.
